text: Arthrosaura montigena is a species of lizard in the family Gymnophthalmidae. It is endemic to Venezuela. ==References== Category:Arthrosaura Category:Reptiles described in 2008 Category:Reptiles of Venezuela Category:Endemic fauna of Venezuela Category:Taxa named by Charles W.
